item.description:
These are all great recommendations. They could have all made a big difference if they had been implemented a couple of decades ago. I’m afraid it’s a bit too late in the day for any meaningful changes when it comes to Academia. Titanic has hit the iceberg a while back, but it’s still chugging along under its own inertia.

